{"tid":1761751,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[眾籌][最後6日!!!] 有手足想幫我地整紀錄片","createTime":"2019-11-29T06:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T13:31:33.000Z","uid":178993,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"03655dc64fe09ee028eafeab36c6adedd38631bd","tid":1761751,"uid":178993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:20:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有手足想幫我地呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">得番唔夠一個星期都仲未過半</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">究竟大家可唔可以推爆佢呢</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原po:<br />\n代朋友po放張自己嘅畫同各位大佬say個sorry先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oz97Efw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOz97Efw.jpg&h=bb961334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位好，我係《2019：夏日宣言》(反送中抗爭紀錄片)嘅導演，我地團隊係一班前線記者、電影工作者、廣告界等人自發組成，早響6月11日開始拍攝，到而家已經紀錄咗接近80日嘅片段。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPZjvnt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPZjvnt.jpg&h=21059a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實眾籌推出咗一段時間，距離目標仍然差好遠。我地冇去硬推，一方面想《催淚之城》嘅眾籌完結先，二黎呢個星期大家嘅心情都好沈重，每一日有手足受傷甚至犧牲，我地根本冇心情推。加上中大保衛戰一役、各大學起義，我地都幾乎不眠不休去不同現場進行拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P16aB2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP16aB2A.jpg&h=bdab6c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但睇住眾籌一日一日咁倒數，我唔甘心，唔想個project做唔落去，所以希望各位有心人可以幫手推上熱門，share出去同支持我地！因為我地想比世界各地嘅人睇到一條屬於香港嘅抗爭紀錄片電影，睇到呢個香港史上嘅光輝足跡！影片長度為90-120分鐘，目標係登上國際影展，各地地區放映，以及Netflix, Amazon Prime Video嗰類國際串流平台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LyQuSA5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLyQuSA5.jpg&h=7ddf3bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗紀錄片之外，我地亦有透過唔同渠道去推動呢場運動，幫手足同文宣(詳情可以睇眾籌)。我地每個人都花上自己所有時間、金錢同器材去做呢個project，加埋後期製作果度要用唔少錢，相信我地捱唔到好耐，缺少資金嘅情況下好難完成。自問對比願意付上性命上前線檔子彈嘅手足，我地嘅付出遠遠比唔上佢地，但我地願意用我地專業技能去為香港貢獻，希望各路有心人可以幫我地順利比條片出世，等咁多日嘅拍攝可以對得住所有手足！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XuLKGuC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXuLKGuC.jpg&h=47779573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反送中抗爭源於炎夏的六月；宣言，是香港人對政權的控訴，以及對世界的吶喊；事件記錄於當年今日2019年，這就是電影名稱的由來。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5sDz3H7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5sDz3H7.jpg&h=3b9bcaf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紀錄片電影 《2019：夏日宣言(The Edge of Liberty) 》眾籌計劃正式推出。<br />\n<br />\n《2019：夏日宣言》是一部關於香港反送中抗爭的紀錄片電影。本片希望以有限的電影長度內，綜合由6月9號起，反送中運動的形成及抗爭過程，以非單元形式，完整呈現給所有本地以及海外觀眾，更加了解事情的來龍去脈，讓世界作一個歷史的參考。<br />\n<br />\n影片透過不同的受訪者講述，還原重要事件及細節，重點帶出反送中運動的核心價值，抗爭升級過程(如遍地開花及開展國際戰線)，展現香港人的創意。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/theedgeofliberty/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftheedgeofliberty%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=399286a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/theedgeofliberty/</a><br />\nIG: teol_hk<br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://www.twitter.com/edgeoflibertyhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2Fedgeoflibertyhk&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=0b70f8db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitter.com/edgeoflibertyhk</a><br />\n預告片: <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aFIJAK_15ZI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaFIJAK_15ZI&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=3bc2f63b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aFIJAK_15ZI</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\nKickstarter眾籌連結: <a href=\"http://kck.st/2Nnkkvk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkck.st%2F2Nnkkvk&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=6d28041f\" target=\"_blank\">http://kck.st/2Nnkkvk</a>"},{"pid":"2662118290a3d45c639cf7f829893424f13bbf3e","tid":1761751,"uid":178993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f00a564caea187d7dc0ade77e44a654dc54ee1","tid":1761751,"uid":178993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後6日</span></span>"},{"pid":"a6efe828d10fbfffe8ffbc01f75849b417fb6899","tid":1761751,"uid":178993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321d1d243333f8e7e477c54de7443c3c9c903a02","tid":1761751,"uid":178993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:22:45.000Z","msg":"手足幫幫手好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987174b98797a99f4b324f3f76dcab8d77b3f050","tid":1761751,"uid":178993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40b1f8df2deca5793705ce5df0e6f7b623f2bc7","tid":1761751,"uid":178993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:24:13.000Z","